&quot;Jhin&rsquo;s crits deal less damage than normal, and his attack speed doesn&rsquo;t actually scale with attack speed. Instead, Jhin gains attack damage from any attack speed and crit chance he earns through itemization and runes, while crits give him a burst of movement based on his attack speed.&quot;

Wouldn&#039;t it have made more sense to put this on Caitlyn and, I don&#039;t know, make her a true precision sniper? Could have done it during the marksman reworks. Would have been great, would have fit, been thematic, a real sniper.

But nah.
